&lt;p&gt;Github linki için &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/0xbekoo/WinKernelDev/tree/main/Virtual_Memory/src&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;buraya&lt;/a&gt; tıklayabilirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;
